dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon data layer represents zoning for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2014.[This dataset includes the local zoning of parcels under Outagamie County Zoning jurisdiction. It also includes Airport zoning.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[The zoning layer was created to be used to identify the local zoning in areas of Outagamie County Zoning jurisdiction as well as the ability to be "linked" to the tax listing database using the PIN as the unique identifier or link. The airport zoning layer is a polygon layer which represents the overlay districts for the Outagamie County Regional Airport.]
